{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idee97df52-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1425a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1425a"},"text":"§ 1425a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Producers of honey; loan obligations and liabilities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idee97df53-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1425a/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Loan forfeiture limitation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A producer of honey may satisfy the producer’s obligation to repay a loan, or a portion of a loan, made to the producer under section 1446h ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002146"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002146"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title by forfeiting the collateral for the loan, or portion of the loan, only if the value of the collateral forfeited, when taken together with the value of the collateral forfeited on any other loan or loans of the person for such crop of honey under section 1446h "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002146"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" of this title, does not exceed $200,000 in the 1991 crop year, $175,000 in the 1992 crop year, $150,000 in the 1993 crop year, and $125,000 in each of the 1994 and subsequent crop years: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided, however","children":[],"tail":", That the loan forfeiture limitation provided by this section shall not be applicable for any crop year for which the Secretary does not permit producers of honey to repay the price support loans at a level determined under section 1446h(b)(2) "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002146"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idee97df54-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1425a/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Liability for nonforfeitable part of obligation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The producer of honey shall be personally liable for the repayment of a loan or loans made to the producer under the program for the crop of honey involved, with respect to that portion of the loan or loans for which satisfaction of the loan by forfeiture, as provided in subsection (a), is prohibited.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idee97df55-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1425a/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Extent of personal liability","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The loan contracts of the Commodity Credit Corporation entered into with producers of honey shall clearly indicate the extent to which a producer of honey may be personally liable for repayment of a loan under this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idee97df56-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1425a/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Promulgation of regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commodity Credit Corporation may issue such regulations as the Corporation deems necessary to carry out this section. The regulations shall provide for the attribution of the value of collateral forfeited on loans described in subsection (a).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idee97df57-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-10-31/ch792"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1949, ch. 792","children":[],"tail":", title IV, § 405A, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/460/tVI/s634/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–460, title VI, § 634(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2263"},"text":"102 Stat. 2263","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/tX/s1002"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, title X, § 1002","children":[],"tail":", title XI, § 1161(d), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-28"},"text":"Nov. 28, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/3490"},"text":"104 Stat. 3490","children":[],"tail":", 3521.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idee97df58-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idee97df59-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idee97df5a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1446h"},"text":"Section 1446h of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (a), was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/127/tI/s171/b/2/H"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–127, title I, § 171(b)(2)(H)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-04-04"},"text":"Apr. 4, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/938"},"text":"110 Stat. 938","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idee97df5b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/s1161/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, § 1161(d)","children":[],"tail":", substituted references to sections 1446h and 1446h(b)(2) of this title for references to sections 1446(b) and 1446(b)(2)(B) of this title, respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/s1002/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, § 1002(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “person for such crop of honey under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1446h"},"text":"section 1446h of this title","children":[],"tail":", does not exceed $200,000 in the 1991 crop year, $175,000 in the 1992 crop year, $150,000 in the 1993 crop year, and $125,000 in each of the 1994 and subsequent crop years” for “producer for such crop of honey under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1446/b"},"text":"section 1446(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":", does not exceed $250,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/s1002/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, § 1002(2)","children":[],"tail":", inserted provisions requiring that the regulations issued pursuant to this subsection provide for the attribution of the value of collateral forfeited on loans described in subsec. (a)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idee97df5c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idee97df5d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1990 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":" effective beginning with 1991 crop of an agricultural commodity, with provision for prior crops, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/s1171"},"text":"section 1171 of Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1421"},"text":"section 1421 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idee97df5e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Inapplicability of Section","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section inapplicable to 2014 through 2018 crops of covered commodities, cotton, and sugar and inapplicable to milk during period beginning ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-02-07"},"text":"Feb. 7, 2014","children":[],"tail":", through "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 2018","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s9092/b/10"},"text":"section 9092(b)(10) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section inapplicable to 2008 through 2012 crops of covered commodities, peanuts, and sugar and in